data.description:
This stunning home located in Garden Park offers an ideal split floor plan with a spacious master suite on one side, featuring trey ceilings for added elegance and a luxurious master bath equipped with a jetted garden tub, separate shower, double vanity, and a generously sized walk-in closet. This three bedrooms and two baths home is designed for comfort and convenience.
The property boasts several recent upgrades, including a BRAND NEW HVAC system installed in 2023, ensuring efficient and reliable heating and cooling. Additionally, the septic line was repaired and the septic tank pumped in the 2023 as well, providing peace of mind to you.
The interior features a spacious family room highlighted by a gas fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings. The floor plan seamlessly connects the family room to the formal dining room, creating an ideal space for entertaining guests or enjoying family meals.
Outside, the home offers a 2-car garage and a HUGE backyard enclosed by a privacy fence, providing ample space for outdoor activities and gatherings.
Conveniently located on a cul-de-sac, this home offers easy access to I-65, shopping, eateries, a Golf Course, YMCA, and it's just minutes away from Maxwell and Gunter Air Force Base.
With its desirable features, prime location, and recent upgrades, this home is sure to attract attention quickly. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity – schedule a showing today with me or your preferred agent before it's gone!!!
